<li><a href="http://wesley.nnu.edu/wesleyan_theology/theojrnl/31-35/31-2-4.htm" class="external text" title="http://wesley.nnu.edu/wesleyan_theology/theojrnl/31-35/31-2-4.htm" rel="nofollow">Theosis &amp; Sanctification: John Wesley's Reformulation of a Patristic Doctrine</a> by Michael Christensen</li>
<li><a href="http://www.imd.gr/html/en/section02/spirlife/resurrection/04/04.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.imd.gr/html/en/section02/spirlife/resurrection/04/04.htm" rel="nofollow">God and Mankind Have Become One Race</a> by NIKOLAOS P. VASSILIADIS</li>
<li><a href="http://www.myriobiblos.gr/texts/english/christou_partakers.html" class="external text" title="http://www.myriobiblos.gr/texts/english/christou_partakers.html" rel="nofollow">Partakers of God</a> by Panayiotis Christou</li>
<li><a href="http://mldb.byu.edu/follett.htm" class="external text" title="http://mldb.byu.edu/follett.htm" rel="nofollow">King Follet Discourse at Brigham Young University</a></li>
<li><a href="http://mormonlit.lib.byu.edu/lit_work.php?w_id=8000" class="external text" title="http://mormonlit.lib.byu.edu/lit_work.php?w_id=8000" rel="nofollow">Journal Of Discourses archive, Brigham Young University</a></li>
</ul>
